[{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2018-02-21-misunderstanding-of-scrum-daily-standing-meeting","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"Ex: Scrum 每日立會容易出現的誤解","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這段敘述對於每日立會所期望的氛團比喻的很道味，特意節錄作為提醒與溫習。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以下摘錄自《Scrum，用一半的時間做兩倍的事》"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-1","ariaDescribedBy":"footnote-label","dataFootnoteRef":true,"id":"user-content-fnref-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我常看到某個意外出現的問題是，大家都傾向於把每日立會當成只是一個向大家報告「我做了這件事⋯⋯我準備做那件事」等個人事項的場合，一個人一講完就輪到下一個人講述。更理想的方式應該接近於美式足球，選手圍在一起商討戰術的景象。外接員可能會說：「那個防守前鋒礙到我了。」聽到這句話，進攻絆鋒可能會說：「他就教給我處裡，我負責突破防線。」或者四分衛可能會說：「我們的跑陣碰到瓶頸，不如出其不意地把球往左傳。」用意在於整個團隊迅速決定如何完成衝刺，取得勝利。被動因應不但懶散，也形同主動拖累團隊裡其他人的表現。一但找出問題點就必須即刻予以排除。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"section","props":{"className":["footnotes"],"dataFootnotes":true},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"className":["sr-only"],"id":"footnote-label"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Footnotes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"江裕真（譯）（2015）。SCRUM：用一半的時間做兩倍的事（原作者：Jeff Sutherland）。臺北市：遠見天下文化。（原著出版年：2014）（117 – 118 頁 ） "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-1","ariaLabel":"Back to content","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":true},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]}]}]}]}]},"title_en":"Misunderstanding of Scrum's Daily Standing Meeting","slug":"misunderstanding-of-scrum-daily-standing-meeting","aliases":["Ex: 